                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/images/Homepage/infochips.jpg" alt="Infochips" class="img-responsive" />
            <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                <p>
                    Infochips<br />
